<Layout title="Wiesbaden Without a Car - Anno 1728" lang="en">
	<div class="page-header">
		<h1>Wiesbaden in One Day Without a Car</h1>
		<p class="subtitle">Explore the state capital by bus and on foot</p>
	</div>

	<div class="intro-box">
		<p>
			<strong>Getting there:</strong> Start at Dernsches Gel√§nde ‚Äì reachable by bus line 21
			from Alt Auringen (approx. 20 minutes) or by bicycle.
		</p>
	</div>

	<section class="itinerary">
		<h2>Your Tour Through Wiesbaden</h2>

		<div class="stop">
			<div class="stop-number">1</div>
			<div class="stop-content">
				<h3>Town Hall & Hessian State Parliament</h3>
				<p>Start at the Town Hall with its miniature model. Across the street, you'll see the Hessian State Parliament.</p>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="stop">
			<div class="stop-number">2</div>
			<div class="stop-content">
				<h3>Market Church</h3>
				<p>Visit the neo-Gothic Market Church ‚Äì Wiesbaden's landmark.</p>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="stop highlight">
			<div class="stop-number">‚òï</div>
