			<div class="stop-content">
				<h3>R√∂mertor & Kochbrunnen</h3>
				<p>Brief visit to the historic sites ‚Äì the Kochbrunnen is one of the hottest thermal springs in Europe.</p>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="stop featured">
			<div class="stop-number">4</div>
			<div class="stop-content">
				<h3>Neroberg Railway</h3>
				<p>Ride the water-powered funicular railway to the Neroberg. Bicycles must be pushed up.</p>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="neroberg-options">
